comments: First performed in the seminfinal of Melodi Grand Prix 1995, which were a part of the program "Æres den som æres bør" at NRK. The Norwegian final was held 1 April 1995, where the performance won the final and became the Norwegian entry to Eurovision Song Contest 1995. It won the ESC in Dublin, despite a lot of criticism, esepcially from Sweden, as the lyrics only contains 24 words and the song in practice is an instrumental.  This was the second victory for Norway in Eurovision Song Contest.
